data.description: This top-floor corner unit in the Sun Rise community presents an enticing opportunity for comfortable living amidst the natural beauty of Ewa Beach.  Situated in a highly sought-after area, residents can enjoy easy access to the Ewwa Town Center and Geiger Community Park, ensuring a balance of urban amenities and outdoor recreation.  Whether you're a first-time homebuyer seeking a cozy retreat, downsizing for a simpler lifestyle, or looking for an investment property in a desirable location, this unit caters to various needs.  For those with a knack for customization, there's ample opportunity for further renovations to tailor the space to your taste and preferences.  Don't let this opportunity slip away - take the chance to make this Ewa Beach gem your own, and experience the joys of island living in paradise!
